      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration fans! This vehicle is a fantastic project car with a ton of potential for the right person to bring it back to its former glory. While it needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a great opportunity to get a rare find at a budget-friendly price and truly make it your own!",
